In Garageband click the loop button.


[[File:Garageband loop.png]]




Then move the yellow ruler bar to where you would like to record a cycle.

[[File:Garageband ruler.png]]




Select the track you want to record to and click the record button

[[File:Garageband record button.png]]




Record your takes. When you are done you will have a track that looks something like the image below.

[[File:Garageband record.png]]




Click the highlighted take count number on the upper left of the recording

[[File:Garageband take count.png]]


[[File:Garageband takes.png]]



You can then select the take you want from the list. You can also delete all unused takes or the selected take.


